headline.print_headline: Supporters of Algeria's Bouteflika Rally for His Re-election
headline.main: Supporters of Algeria's Bouteflika Rally for His Re-election

lead_paragraph: Several thousand supporters of Algerian President Abdelaziz Bouteflika rallied on Saturday to support his re-election bid in a show of strength by those who portray him as key to stability in the North African country.
